<lb n="1"/>śrī mānudgaṭavīra mau
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ḷīśaparatpādāra vindapra
<lb n="3" break="no"/>bhuḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> nāmānyāgōsaraṇā
